{
  "chapter": 40,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十回「病美人」。芮玮向药王爷请教牛毛天王针的来历，得知此暗器乃天山玉面神婆一派独传，手法已至炉火纯青。药王爷讲完自身故事后离去，留下芮玮在药铺研读扁鹊遗下的医学奇书。林琼菊默默陪伴，半年间照顾简怀萱起居，任劳任怨。芮玮日夜用功，终于配成解药服下，并向林琼菊托付简怀萱的照料。半年后药王爷不告而别，掌柜传达其安排。忽有麻衣、白衣二老抬暖轿求医，轿中坐着一位全身肌肤鲜红的绝色病美人。芮玮诊出她中了参毒，正欲施治，却见轿旁之人竟是曾配毒害他的史不旧。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "晚辈尚有一事请教前辈。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "药王爷",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你有何不解之事。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "那日晚辈听到前辈说牛毛天王针，不知牛毛天王针现今是何人惯使的暗器？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "药王爷",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你问这做什？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "晚辈曾被一女子用针形暗器救了一命，心想也许就是前辈说的牛毛天王针。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "药王爷",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那女子是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "她就是大师伯的后裔。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "药王爷",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "牛毛天王针不是刘家暗器，当今武林中以牛毛天王针为暗器者，只有天山玉面神婆一派，牛毛天王针不似梅花针轻易可以练成，非有绝妙手法与内功者，甚难练得成功。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "莫非她是天山玉面神婆的弟子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "药王爷",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "玉面神婆性情古怪，没听说收过弟子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "这么说来，会是谁用牛毛天王针驱散在街上高喊‘失心女’的人群？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "药王爷",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "以当时的情况看，那发射牛毛天王针的手法已达炉火纯青的地步，我想只有玉面神婆才能做到。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "玉面神婆为何要用牛毛天王针驱散人群？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "药王爷",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "玉面神婆的行径一向奇怪，她发针驱散人群，实难猜测有何用意。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她不可能认识我呀？她不可能认识简怀萱……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "药王爷",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不要再胡思乱想啦，你把爱妻抛在外房这么久没有去理会，不怕她怪你吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "她不是我妻子……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "药王爷",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不是你妻子也是最最要好的女友，我去请她进来。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你们一上午谈些什么，不能让我也来听听？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "药王爷讲了个故事，那故事叙他一生，他老人家一生坎坷不平，惋转凄恻，令人听来心酸不已。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "难怪我在外房听到药王爷的哭声，是不是他叙到伤心处痛哭起来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这么大年纪的人痛哭失声，想来他那一生也真悲苦了，大哥，你能说说给我听吗？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "好的，有时间我说来你听。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "她的病好了没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "只能说好了一半，还有一半没好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "她也真可怜，大哥半年内又要找人驱去内毒，又要去帮她寻访三眼秀士，时间怎么可能？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "药王爷借我一册医学奇书，我想在半年内找一个安静所在，研究医术自配出解药出来，然后天涯飘泊寻访三眼秀士。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那是一册什么书？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "是战国名医扁鹊遗下的，我只要在半年内能够研究通，定然可以解去自身之毒。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "倘苦研究不通呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "这是个以两人一生为赌的赌注，赢了我与怀萱皆有救，若不能赢我死了，怀萱流落无依，谁来照顾她……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "我有一事请你答应。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "可是要我来照顾简怀萱？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你照顾她，送到药王爷这里，请他设法医治，若是药王爷也无法找到三眼秀士，你带她回黑堡，求你父亲给她口闲饭吃。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这件事？你不要托我去办。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "为什么，你不愿意或是……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥死了，我也不想再活。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lao_shu",
      "speaker_name": "小老鼠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "送到里面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lao_shu",
      "speaker_name": "小老鼠",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "‘咱们大老板从斜对面酒楼叫来一桌菜，说请你们三位好好吃一顿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lao_shu",
      "text": "请你们大老板也来吃呀。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lao_shu",
      "speaker_name": "小老鼠",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大老板早走啦，说你们要在这儿住半年。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lao_shu",
      "text": "真的走了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "掌柜",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我们老板走了好一会了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_gui",
      "text": "他老人家去何处？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "掌柜",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不知道，老板说来就来，说去就去，谁也不知道他现在要到何处，总之五个地方，他随意走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_gui",
      "text": "他可留下话来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "掌柜",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "老板去时交待，要你们住在这里，说我们这里三位大夫医术尚佳，相公研究医术有不懂之处可请教他们三位。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_gui",
      "text": "你们老板好意我接受啦，我们住在这里有麻烦之处，尚请多多包涵。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "掌柜",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "哪里，哪里，相公尽管安心住下，有什么事叫我们来做就是。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你静下心来说，有什么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老头",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "再不请药王爷出来，咱们哥俩拆房子啦。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "白衣老头",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "药王爷有什么见不得人，咱们有事求见，躲着算那门子？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_lao_tou",
      "text": "你们有什么事要见药王爷？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "白衣老头",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "治病呀，找他老人家除了治病还有什么找头。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_lao_tou",
      "text": "药王爷不在这里？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老头",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你是什么人，要你来说话？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_lao_tou",
      "text": "我是药王爷的记名弟子。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "白衣老头",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那好啊，请你师父出来见见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_lao_tou",
      "text": "我说过，他老人家不在。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 40,
